Okay, everyone ready?

294
00:23:54,840 --> 00:23:55,840
Listen for my cue.

295
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:57,600
We'll count down from five.

296
00:23:58,800 --> 00:23:59,600
Five.

297
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:00,560
Four.

298
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,480
Three.

299
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:02,320
Two.

300
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:03,240
One.

301
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:46,920
Oh my goodness

302
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:48,840
My back, my back's giving out

303
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,400
Come on, come on, take a quick break

304
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,440
Take a break, rest for a bit

305
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:55,800
Oh my goodness

306
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,760
You be careful too

307
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,080
You've even had surgery on that back of yours

308
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,960
I've been quite happy working today

309
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:15,920
That's great

310
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,840
The weather's been just perfect

311
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:20,600
It's another bountiful harvest year

312
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:24,400
Take a look

313
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:27,960
Look at how sturdy these rice stalks are

314
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:30,840
The pulp pounded from stalks like these

315
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:33,800
is absolutely top-grade

316
00:25:34,280 --> 00:25:34,880
Yongnian

317
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:38,600
Wouldn't you say life like this is good?

318
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,680
Let me tell you how I truly feel

319
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:42,480
I often think to myself

320
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:44,920
Our ancestors from eight generations back

321
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:48,000
never dreamed their descendants

322
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:51,160
could ever live such a beautiful and happy life today

323
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:58,800
The birds in the trees pair off two by two

324
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:05,480
The green hills and clear waters wear a smile

325
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:12,280
Reach out and pluck a single flower

326
00:26:42,720 --> 00:26:44,440
Hey, keep an eye on things for me later, okay?

327
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:44,840
Sure.

328
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:45,880
Here I go.

329
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:53,400
Here we go.

330
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:55,680
Come on, come on.

331
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:56,080
Brother.

332
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,760
Sis, come over and sit down.

333
00:27:00,760 --> 00:27:01,440
Like this.

334
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:02,960
A little to the right.

335
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,520
I'll fill in the blank for you.

336
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:05,320
No, no, no.

337
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:06,560
I've been practicing for ages.

338
00:27:06,560 --> 00:27:07,400
No good, no good, no good.

339
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,040
Why is it no good?

340
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:08,760
Come on, why is it no good?

341
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:10,440
Brother Xiao Min, don't fall for his trick.

342
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,360
Look at what he wrote.

343
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,320
Just look at his writing.

344
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:13,920
Come on, whether I write it or my dad does, isn't it the same?

345
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,800
Xiao Min, that doesn't sound reliable to me either.

346
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,800
Dad, let me do it for you.

347
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:17,320
No, no.

348
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:17,960
Xiao Xing, come here, good.

349
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:18,840
You definitely can't write it.

350
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:20,160
None of you are qualified

351
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:21,320
to write this name.

352
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:22,520
Only my Master can.

353
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:24,680
Xiao Min, you'd better think this through.

354
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:25,680
Your Master

355
00:27:25,800 --> 00:27:27,760
isn't even as educated as Xiao Xing.

356
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:29,000
You'd really better think it over.

357
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,400
Once this is written,

358
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:32,240
it'll be passed down for generations.

359
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:33,600
Think it through.

360
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:35,080
You talk too much.

361
00:27:35,560 --> 00:27:37,760
Isn't this just like taking an ID photo?

362
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:38,680
What's going on?

363
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:40,760
Master, isn't that right?

364
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:42,960
Master.

365
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,560
Your name isn't filled in yet.

366
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,040
Not yet, come on.

367
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:46,960
Then let me fill it in for you.

368
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:47,600
Okay.

369
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:51,960
Don't laugh.

370
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,160
What are you laughing at?

371
00:28:00,600 --> 00:28:01,480
Laughing at Xiao Min.

372
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,520
Laugh, laugh.

373
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:06,760
Laughing because I'm happy, so happy.

374
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:07,320
Well then, Xiao Min.

375
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:08,320
I, I said it already.

376
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:10,760
Master, Master, Master.

377
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,240
Are they laughing out of joy?

378
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:14,160
She's happy too.

379
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,520
Then I'll write it for you.

380
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:19,400
Master.

381
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:23,480
Do you want to practice on this first?

382
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,480
Why?

383
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,720
My dad's just afraid you won't write it well.

384
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:30,320
Well or not, I'll accept it, Master.

385
00:28:30,320 --> 00:28:32,760
Fine, whoever you think writes it well,

386
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,480
go find someone else to write it.

387
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,400
No, no, Master, Master.

388
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,360
That's not what I meant.

389
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:37,080
This name

390
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:38,760
can only be written by you.

391
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,560
Is he right?

392
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:46,400
All right, I'll listen to her.

393
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:53,960
Present

394
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:54,960
the Apprenticeship petition.

395
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:57,360
Master,

396
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:02,560
return the apprentice's petition.

397
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:12,120
Bestow

398
00:29:12,120 --> 00:29:13,800
the named paper curtain.

399
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,040
Thank you, Master.

400
00:29:37,520 --> 00:29:38,360
Serve the tea.

401
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:47,400
Master, please have some tea.

402
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:54,760
Madam, please have some tea.

403
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,480
Perform the apprenticeship rite.

404
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,720
Pass down the ancestral teachings

405
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,680
Name a successor

406
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,600
Today, I appoint Zhang Du

407
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:39,920
as the 36th-generation heir of Xuan Family Papermaking

408
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:43,200
For generations, our family has honored Wingceltis bark

409
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:45,520
befriended Sandy Field Rice Straw

410
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:49,040
and taken the mountain springs as a mirror

411
00:30:49,040 --> 00:30:52,680
Inheriting the snow-bathed bones of Wingceltis

412
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:56,240
carrying the nine-tempered soul of rice straw

413
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:59,040
we craft Xuan paper that endures a thousand years

414
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:02,400
Today I pass down seven ancestral precepts

415
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:06,160
May the heirs of future generations

416
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,520
engrave them upon their hearts

417
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,520
This disciple listens with reverence

418
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:18,720
First: uphold righteousness

419
00:31:20,280 --> 00:31:21,640
Wingceltis and rice straw

420
00:31:22,320 --> 00:31:23,880
through a thousand hammerings and refinements

421
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:26,600
soaked and sun-dried through the seasons

422
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:31,400
shed all rawness to gain jade-like bones

423
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:36,240
A person in this world must also cleanse their heart with clear springs

424
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,280
Take the white stone as one's aim

425
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:40,480
cast off the false, keep the true

426
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:43,000
only then attain uprightness

427
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:47,000
Xuan paper is pure white as snow, never to be stained

428
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:51,440
and so should the human heart be

429
00:31:52,760 --> 00:31:54,440
Second: strive for exquisite craft

430
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:58,040
Sheet forming ten thousand times, never wearying of the toil

431
00:31:58,360 --> 00:32:02,040
Tending the drying fire a thousand times, never sparing fatigue

432
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,280
Everything that becomes a fine work

433
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:09,440
must pass three steamings and nine boilings, straining sinew and bone

434
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:13,200
Third: cherish materials

435
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,960
Wingceltis takes three years to mature

436
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:18,920
rice straw is tempered through the hottest days of summer

437
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:22,440
Use materials as if tending your own kin

438
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:25,000
never squander the gifts of heaven and earth

439
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:28,600
Craft your wares with lasting reverence

440
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:31,520
never dishonor the craftsmanship of our ancestors

441
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:34,560
Fourth: pass on the flame

442
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:37,080
Making Xuan paper takes 108 steps

443
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:39,360
each step holds its own secret

444
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:42,960
Sooner lose ten fingers than lose a single skill

445
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:47,520
Sooner end the bloodline than teach the unworthy

446
00:32:47,800 --> 00:32:50,120
Fifth: still the mind

447
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:54,360
A restless heart makes the curtain's waves unruly

448
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:58,000
an impatient nature scatters the paper's clouds

449
00:32:58,440 --> 00:33:00,360
Practicing the craft is like Zen meditation

450
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:03,960
haste over the fire yields no true flavor

451
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:06,640
Sixth: keep to simplicity

452
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:10,000
Envy not the splendor of fine brocade

453
00:33:10,520 --> 00:33:13,160
covet not the shortcuts of speculation

454
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:15,880
hold fast to the plain and genuine essence

455
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:19,320
Long-lived paper, after a thousand years, returns to plainness

456
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:22,680
in the ink's endless shifts, the heart is finally seen

457
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:25,760
Seventh: embrace and contain

458
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:28,720
Xuan paper readily takes in ink and water

459
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:32,680
bearing the weight of thick and thin, dry and wet

460
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,720
Be a person open and humble as a valley

461
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:38,160
embracing all glory and shame, gain and loss

462
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:41,240
Within the curtain's grain hide hills and ravines

463
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:44,960
upon the jade-plate sheet, all beings find passage

464
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:48,680
The people of our paper land must firmly remember

465
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:51,560
In sheet forming, sink the heart and keep the stillness

466
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:54,280
in the drying fire, banish restlessness and keep the truth

467
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:57,480
Water and fire forge the paper's spirit

468
00:33:58,000 --> 00:34:01,120
and time casts the craftsman's soul

469
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:02,000
Good

470
00:34:40,159 --> 00:34:41,080
Dear everyone,

471
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:42,840
folks and neighbors of our Taohua Town,

472
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,920
and colleagues from our e-commerce base,

473
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:50,239
and all the honored guests who've graced

474
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:51,719
our launch ceremony today,

475
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,400
thank you all for coming.

476
00:34:54,199 --> 00:34:55,480
Because today, we've all

477
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:59,320
gathered here out of love for Taohua Town

478
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:02,760
and love for Xuan paper.

479
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:05,280
Today I'm truly overwhelmed with emotion.

480
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,960
Standing here,

481
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,240
as far as the eye can see,

482
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:13,800
are Wingceltis forests nurtured by towering mountains,

483
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:16,720
and nourished by the gentle spring waters,

484
00:35:16,720 --> 00:35:18,560
the thousand-year-old ancient craft:

485
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:19,600
Xuan paper.

486
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:22,760
This cultural treasure that lasts a thousand years

487
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:25,080
is the soul of our Taohua Town,

488
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:27,920
and the very gene flowing through the veins

489
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:31,480
of every single one of our townsfolk.

490
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:33,000
For thousands of years,

491
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:37,920
our Xuan paper artisans have chosen one craft for a lifetime,

492
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:41,640
using their persistence, wisdom, and sweat

493
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:44,560
to guard this intangible heritage craft,

494
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:46,320
letting each and every sheet

495
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:48,760
of Xuan paper, bearing Chinese tradition,

496
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:52,000
go from here out into the world.

497
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:55,400
Today, our era is surging forward.

498
00:35:56,680 --> 00:35:57,800
We're now living in an age

499
00:35:57,800 --> 00:36:01,440
where AI is sweeping across the globe.

500
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:03,800
So how can we make

501
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:06,640
this traditional Xuan paper industry of ours

502
00:36:06,640 --> 00:36:08,800
shine brilliantly in this

503
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:10,560
ever-changing era?

504
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:12,160
As you all know,

505
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:15,240
this has long troubled us,

506
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:17,880
a question we've painstakingly pondered.

507
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,240
What you're all seeing today,

508
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,640
the launch of our e-commerce base,

509
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:28,400
is our resounding answer after careful thought,

510
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:32,360
our answer of proactively seeking change.

511
00:36:33,080 --> 00:36:36,480
It's also us actively embracing the roaring

512
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,560
spring tide of this era.

513
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:39,880
Students, what we're now visiting

514
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:42,440
is one of the steps in making Xuan paper.

515
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:43,720
It's called paper drying.

516
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:08,480
Your dad passed it to Zhang Du. Aren't you jealous?

517
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,080
Having you is enough for me.

518
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:13,520
Lin Yiran.

519
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:17,600
What are you doing?

520
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,400
Hello, Teacher Jiang.

521
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:54,240
Uncle Xuan.

522
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:56,360
Where's your father?

523
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:00,320
He's already passed away.

524
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,600
When did it happen?

525
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:11,480
A month ago.

526
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,320
He lived his whole life with dignity.

527
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,520
He didn't want anyone to see him

528
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:18,000
in the final stages of his illness.

529
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:25,280
Uncle Xuan, please, come inside.

530
00:38:25,680 --> 00:38:26,520
All right.

531
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:55,080
Uncle Xuan

532
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:59,240
This is what my father wanted you to see

533
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,280
His final painting

534
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,400
Uncle Xuan

535
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,200
This is the letter

536
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:53,800
my father left for you

537
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,800
To create this painting,

538
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:02,800
my father spent five months

539
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:04,640
For these five months,

540
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:07,240
he moved his sickroom here

541
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:09,080
Throughout this half-year of work,

542
00:40:09,680 --> 00:40:11,520
he was often exhausted beyond his limits

543
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:13,800
He often kept saying

544
00:40:14,160 --> 00:40:15,360
that if he couldn't paint it well,

545
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,080
he'd be failing himself

546
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,320
and failing this paper too

547
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:38,160
Yongnian, you wild scholar, may this letter greet you like the vast sea.

548
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:42,400
At this moment, my brush hovers above the peak of endless mountains and rivers.

549
00:40:42,560 --> 00:40:46,520
A thousand peaks of ink surge beneath my brush tip.

550
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:49,320
Gazing across the land, by the Qingyi River,

551
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:53,720
I still see you barefoot in waist-deep icy water,

552
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:55,240
gathering Wingceltis bark.

553
00:40:55,640 --> 00:41:00,120
and cursed me as a mere painter who knew nothing of the land's bones.

554
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:07,640
Now behold this thirty-thousand-mile expanse of misty ink.

555
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:12,520
Finally worthy of vindicating your Three-Zhang-Three.

556
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:16,640
Though I can no longer quarrel with you now,

557
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:20,080
I see the Yellow River winding through this scroll,

558
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:22,200
and in its waves still churns

559
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:24,960
the spittle of our forty years of arguing.

560
00:41:25,120 --> 00:41:28,040
Amid the ranges of Mount Tai and the Kunlun,

561
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:34,000
still echo the absurd curses we hurled across the miles.

562
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:37,440
Tonight at midnight, when the river surges highest,

563
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:39,720
I'll leave a blank space on the cliffs of Kuimen Gorge.

564
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:43,000
That is your tomb, your hanging coffin.

565
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:45,360
If you meet Meng Po on the road to the underworld,

566
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,480
just knock over her bowl of broth.

567
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:51,160
Next life, mix my ashes into your paper,

568
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:53,680
and I'll splash ink blended with your soul.

569
